"we"--me, tom, the kids.

127
00:06:18,230 --> 00:06:20,700
That family you've come to know and love.

128
00:06:20,730 --> 00:06:22,300
All seven of you?

129
00:06:22,330 --> 00:06:23,430
Yeah.

130
