Hey, actually, um, since you're here,

178
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:49,600
I was thinking that maybe it would be a good idea

179
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:52,430
To tell orson about mike's, you know...

180
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,760
Drug problem.

181
